  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Source<String,String[]>

    public class GoogleWebMasterSourceDaily
extends QueryBasedSource<String,String[]>
    The logic of calculating the watermarks in this GoogleWebMasterSourceDaily only works with the configuration below: source.querybased.watermark.type=hour source.querybased.partition.interval=24
